Clean Code


Separation of Concerns(SoC)
 - Easier to Maintain
 - Easier to Extend
 - Reuse More Code
 - Easier to Test
 - Easier to Isolate Bugs
The Rule of One
 - A Component has one Role
 - One Component per file
 - Singular perpose
-------------------------------------

 How :
   -  1 Component , 1 Rule , 1 File
   -  Use Dependencies
   -  Modularize code

Adv
  -  Decreases risk, cost, time to deliver
  -  Increaases testability, code reuse, maintainability
